---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout 
  title="About Us | Your Trusted Product Review Source"
  description="Learn about our mission to provide honest, detailed product reviews and affiliate recommendations."
>
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-16 max-w-4xl">
    <article class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
      <h1>About Us</h1>
      
      <p class="lead">
        Welcome to our affiliate marketing website! We are dedicated to providing you with 
        honest, comprehensive product reviews and recommendations to help you make informed 
        purchasing decisions.
      </p>

      <h2>Our Mission</h2>
      <p>
        Our mission is simple: to help you find the best products that meet your needs and 
        budget. We thoroughly research and test products (when possible) or analyze user 
        reviews, expert opinions, and product specifications to bring you accurate, unbiased 
        information.
      </p>

      <h2>How We Review Products</h2>
      <p>
        Every product review on our site is carefully crafted with attention to detail. We 
        consider factors such as:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>Product quality and build</li>
        <li>Value for money</li>
        <li>User reviews and ratings</li>
        <li>Features and specifications</li>
        <li>Pros and cons</li>
        <li>Alternatives and comparisons</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Affiliate Disclosure</h2>
      <p>
        This website contains affiliate links. When you make a purchase through our affiliate 
        links, we may earn a commission at no additional cost to you. This helps us maintain 
        the site and continue providing free, valuable content.
      </p>
      <p>
        Please note that:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>We only recommend products we genuinely believe in</li>
        <li>Our reviews are honest and independent</li>
        <li>Affiliate relationships do not influence our recommendations</li>
        <li>You never pay more when using our affiliate links</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Contact Us</h2>
      <p>
        Have a question or suggestion? We'd love to hear from you! Please visit our 
        <a href="/contact">contact page</a> to get in touch.
      </p>

      <h2>Thank You</h2>
      <p>
        Thank you for visiting our site. We hope you find our reviews helpful and informative. 
        Your trust is important to us, and we're committed to maintaining the highest standards 
        of honesty and transparency.
      </p>
    </article>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

